itemNotes.Gold Hachiman Do: '+5% Movement Speed' is a unique attribute and it has it's own ability name, titled 'Feathers'. Unique attributes do not stack unlike normal attributes.
itemNotes.Shichimen Tennyo: '+8% Movement Speed' is actually 'Yatagarasu: +8% Movement Speed'. It is a unique attribute and does not stack with other similarly named or valued attributes.
